data.description: Welcome Home to this MOVE IN READY, all brick, single story Perry home located in Canyon Village, Westheimer Lakes. The extended foyer and 12' ceilings invite you into the open concept living space featuring tile and laminate floors throughout.  The large formal dining room could be used as an office, additional living space or game room.   An oversized breakfast bar with, granite counters, is the perfect place to entertain as it connects both the kitchen and main living areas. The primary suite is separate from the additional bedrooms, providing privacy, and includes an ensuite with dual sinks, separate tub and shower and walk-in closet.  Outside you will find an oversized covered patio that backs to a green space with no back neighbors.  The home includes a water softener and is pre-wired for a generator.  Schedule your showing TODAY to see what this home has to offer!
